5:000011127	6:gr-11127	3:The Chronicles of Narnia (The Chronicles of Narnia, #1-7)	4:book review	60:The Chronicles of Narnia (The Chronicles of Narnia, #1-7)	61:C.S. Lewis	62:2014	64:HarperCollins	68:read	69:1998-01-01	63:9780066238500	67:4/5	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/11127
