5:011594337	6:gr-11594337	3:The One and Only Ivan	4:book review	60:The One and Only Ivan	61:Katherine Applegate	62:2012	64:HarperCollins	68:read	69:2022-06-15	63:9780061992254	67:3/5	70:This book has heavy "Charlotte's Web" vibes. Not only are the stories similar by subject but also in theme and character motivations. There's a lot to like about the first person Gorilla perspective. The gentle nature and protective desire of a silverback are present through everything.\n\nI'd recommend this book to the same audience that enjoys Charlotte's Web, Watership Down, and other animal-centric metaphor stories. It fits right in.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/11594337
