5:011737387	6:gr-11737387	3:Fated (Alex Verus, #1)	4:book review	60:Fated (Alex Verus, #1)	61:Benedict Jacka	62:2012	64:Ace	68:read	69:2021-12-22	63:9781937007294	67:3/5	70:Pretty strong start to this series. It has some rough spots but also the hallmarks of a world that's going to get more clear and interesting with each book. I'm going to enjoy tearing through these.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/11737387
