5:001349956	6:gr-1349956	3:The Velveteen Rabbit	4:book review	60:The Velveteen Rabbit	61:Margery Williams Bianco	62:1995	64:Smithmark	68:read	69:1988-01-01	63:9780831791186	67:2/5	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1349956
