5:000144349	6:gr-144349	3:The Burning Bridge (Ranger's Apprentice, #2)	4:book review	60:The Burning Bridge (Ranger's Apprentice, #2)	61:John Flanagan	62:2006	64:Viking Books for Young Readers	68:read	69:2022-06-04	63:9780399244551	67:4/5	70:Wow, what an action packed ending, and one significant cliffhanger. This book was better than the first with the characters continuing to develop and grow. The underlying menace of the world is at the fore and the stakes are high. An excellent YA read.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/144349
