5:017920175	6:gr-17920175	3:Wayward (Wayward Pines, #2)	4:book review	60:Wayward (Wayward Pines, #2)	61:Blake Crouch	62:2013	64:Thomas & Mercer	68:read	69:2015-10-21	63:9781477808702	67:2/5	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/17920175
