5:001812457	6:gr-1812457	3:The Shack	4:book review	60:The Shack	61:William Paul Young	62:2007	64:Windblown Media	68:read	69:2008-01-01	63:9780964729230	67:3/5	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/1812457
