5:183222153	6:gr-183222153	3:Third Eye	4:book review	60:Third Eye	61:Felicia Day	62:2023	64:Audible Originals	68:read	69:2023-11-05	67:3/5	70:This was a pretty cute YA story with a really great cast. It played with the genre tropes in nice ways and had some strong character voices. A few of the very core characters displayed growth through the story, and there were a couple nice twists.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/183222153
