5:022328546	6:gr-22328546	3:Red Queen (Red Queen, #1)	4:book review	60:Red Queen (Red Queen, #1)	61:Victoria Aveyard	62:2015	64:HarperTeen	68:read	69:2017-08-27	67:1/5	70:I liked the beginning, even with the similarities to any number of other books. Once the plot got moving, though, the story got away from the author. Motivations were strained until they didn't make any sense. Betrayals only worked on the surface. Overly powerful characters avoided using their powers to discover the poor plotting of the main characters because... luck, I guess?	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/22328546
