5:002334538	6:gr-2334538	3:Quarter Share (Golden Age of the Solar Clipper, #1)	4:book review	60:Quarter Share (Golden Age of the Solar Clipper, #1)	61:Nathan Lowell	62:2007	64:Nathan Lowell	68:read	69:2014-09-08	67:4/5	70:It's rare to encounter a book where there's really no tension or conflict. It's more rare when that's enjoyable. I'm going to binge the rest of this series in a bit of a feel-good sci-fi cleanse. Soon it will be back to grey characters and broken dreams. Alas.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2334538
