5:023379244	6:gr-23379244	3:The Hidden Masters of Marandur (The Pillars of Reality, #2)	4:book review	60:The Hidden Masters of Marandur (The Pillars of Reality, #2)	61:Jack Campbell	62:2015	64:Audible Studios on Brilliance Audio	68:read	63:9781491540145	67:4/5	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/23379244
