5:002767052	6:gr-2767052	3:The Hunger Games (The Hunger Games, #1)	4:book review	60:The Hunger Games (The Hunger Games, #1)	61:Suzanne Collins	62:2008	64:Scholastic Press	68:read	69:2011-08-30	63:9780439023481	67:4/5	70:Very exciting, through and through. It held me captive in a way a good book should. Sadly, the ending of book one seemed too sudden. I know the series continues, but I wish there was a bit more temporary resolution. No matter. I'm looking forward to the rest.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2767052
