5:002890090	6:gr-2890090	3:The Republic of Thieves (Gentleman Bastard, #3)	4:book review	60:The Republic of Thieves (Gentleman Bastard, #3)	61:Scott Lynch	62:2013	64:Del Rey	68:read	69:2014-04-15	63:9780553804690	67:2/5	70:This book was a bit of a let down. The characters we've come to love didn't have very much to do as their opponents were either God-like in their power, or so meaningless as to offer no challenge. The love story was completely annoying and repetitive and I found myself just wanting the series to end.  The worst possible outcome happened, of course, when I realized that this isn't the final book in the series. It drives me crazy when I don't finish a whole series, but I think this is going to be one of those.\n\nIn short, book 1 was fantastic. Book 2 was a bit scattered, but finished well. Book 3 was a waste of my time.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/2890090
