5:031306843	6:gr-31306843	3:Hydrogen Sleets: a Montague Portal novel	4:book review	60:Hydrogen Sleets: a Montague Portal novel	61:Michael Warren Lucas	62:2016	64:Tilted Windmill Press	68:read	69:2023-01-07	67:4/5	70:These short stories are a blast. We get to explore strange new universes and experience thrilling terror all at the same time. Instead of acrophobia this time it's baraphobia (fear of gravity; yeah I looked it up) at the helm. This story also left me craving Congolese food. Double-win.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/31306843
