5:032177647	6:gr-32177647	3:The Rodek Less Traveled (Black Ocean 4.6)	4:book review	60:The Rodek Less Traveled (Black Ocean 4.6)	61:J.S. Morin	62:2015	64:Magical Scribner Press	68:read	69:2023-03-07	67:3/5	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/32177647
