5:034002132	6:gr-34002132	3:Oathbringer (The Stormlight Archive, #3)	4:book review	60:Oathbringer (The Stormlight Archive, #3)	61:Brandon Sanderson	62:2017	64:Tor Books	68:read	69:2020-01-16	63:9780765326379	67:5/5	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/34002132
