5:035253835	6:gr-35253835	3:Witch Is Why The Owl Returned (A Witch P.I. Mystery #21)	4:book review	60:Witch Is Why The Owl Returned (A Witch P.I. Mystery #21)	61:Adele Abbott	62:2017	64:Implode Publishing Ltd	68:read	69:2021-07-30	67:3/5	70:I think these books are legitimately getting better. The plots entwine a tiny bit more and there's far less incidence of the author forgetting rules she established earlier. This one was enjoyable as always, but a total tease in terms of the larger hinted plot.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/35253835
