5:000355963	6:gr-355963	3:Secrets: On the Ethics of Concealment and Revelation	4:book review	60:Secrets: On the Ethics of Concealment and Revelation	61:Sissela Bok	62:1989	64:Vintage	68:read	69:2020-02-04	63:9780679724735	67:5/5	70:I'm going to add this book to the list of "books that so thoroughly cover a concept that I'm never going to argue about it again but rather send people a copy of this instead." I can't recommend this enough for literally everyone. So many fallacies and social-media arguments are undermined so thoroughly in these pages I can't even begin to list them all. Do yourself a favor and put this in the to-read pile.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/355963
