5:037173003	6:gr-37173003	3:Ms. Marvel, Vol. 9: Teenage Wasteland	4:book review	60:Ms. Marvel, Vol. 9: Teenage Wasteland	61:G. Willow Wilson	62:2018	64:Marvel	68:read	69:2022-01-02	63:9781302910785	67:4/5	70:I really liked this book despite Ms Marvel not appearing for half of it. There were some sappy bits and the villains didn't take center stage. Instead we got family and friendship development, love budding, and reunification. Oh, and it was pretty funny too!	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/37173003
