5:000048855	6:gr-48855	3:The Diary of a Young Girl	4:book review	60:The Diary of a Young Girl	61:Anne Frank	62:1993	64:Bantam	68:read	69:1992-01-01	67:3/5	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/48855
5:048982218	6:gr-48982218	3:The Science of Sci-Fi: From Warp Speed to Interstellar Travel	4:book review	60:The Science of Sci-Fi: From Warp Speed to Interstellar Travel	61:Erin  Macdonald	62:2019	64:Audible Original	68:read	69:2020-03-10	67:2/5	70:I don't think this book really got the right mix of science and sci-fi at any point. The explanations were okay for some of the scientific pieces, but some of the more advanced concepts felt a bit rushed. The sci-fi bits were met with enthusiasm by the author, but not enough analysis and exploration.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/48982218
5:048994289	6:gr-48994289	3:The Flying Flamingo Sisters	4:book review	60:The Flying Flamingo Sisters	61:Carrie Seim	62:2019	64:Audible Original	68:read	69:2020-05-10	67:4/5	70:This audio book is all about the acting and sound design. The story is simple and charming, the characters colorful and silly, but it all comes alive with the full cast recording. My son is a fan, as am I. This lovely little audio drama is worth a few hours listen.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/48994289
