5:000504924	6:gr-504924	3:The Sacrilege (SPQR, #3)	4:book review	60:The Sacrilege (SPQR, #3)	61:John Maddox Roberts	62:1999	64:Minotaur Books	68:read	69:2016-11-26	63:9780312246976	67:5/5	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/504924
5:050548197	6:gr-50548197	3:A Deadly Education (The Scholomance, #1)	4:book review	60:A Deadly Education (The Scholomance, #1)	61:Naomi Novik	62:2020	64:Del Rey	68:read	69:2021-01-15	63:9780593128480	67:5/5	70:What a treat! This isn't magic school trope. It feels more like The Call then Rowling. Great round characters and intricate multifaceted relationships. Incredible world building. I'm so ready for the next book.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/50548197
