5:051190882	6:gr-51190882	3:The Empress of Salt and Fortune (The Singing Hills Cycle, #1)	4:book review	60:The Empress of Salt and Fortune (The Singing Hills Cycle, #1)	61:Nghi Vo	62:2020	64:Tor.com	68:read	69:2023-03-28	67:5/5	70:This book is delightful! I mean, don't get me wrong. There's some heart hurty bits, but even so. It really reminds me of A Psalm for the Wild Built. If you liked that you'll probably love this.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/51190882
