5:000639787	6:gr-639787	3:The Murder on the Links (Hercule Poirot, #2)	4:book review	60:The Murder on the Links (Hercule Poirot, #2)	61:Agatha Christie	62:1984	64:Berkley	68:read	69:2012-07-12	63:9780425067949	67:5/5	70:Another wonderful read. Agatha Christie is quickly becoming my cleanser for the ever present bad fiction I come across, much like coffee beans are for olfactory habituation.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/639787
