5:007090447	6:gr-7090447	3:The Red Pyramid (The Kane Chronicles, #1)	4:book review	60:The Red Pyramid (The Kane Chronicles, #1)	61:Rick Riordan	62:2010	64:Disney Hyperion	68:read	69:2017-05-26	63:9781423113386	67:1/5	70:Review of the audiobook:\n\nThe female reader was fantastic with great energy and accents. The male reader was fair. The story was not well crafted and the plot boring. I made it about 70% before abandoning it.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/7090447
