5:078786087	6:gr-78786087	3:Oathbound Healer (Beneath the Dragoneye Moons, #1)	4:book review	60:Oathbound Healer (Beneath the Dragoneye Moons, #1)	61:Selkie Myth	62:2020	68:read	69:2023-03-15	67:3/5	70:I was skeptical going into this book, and I actually had two false-starts. The reincarnation aspect of a lit-rpg has failed to capture my interest several times in the past and this seemed destined to follow suit. I tried once more, though, and made it beyond that initial hurdle only to find some characters worth caring about.\n\nThis genre is not my favorite. I really love The Wandering Inn, and now this series seems to be joining the limited ranks.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/78786087
