5:000867247	6:gr-867247	3:A Book of Five Rings: The Classic Guide to Strategy	4:book review	60:A Book of Five Rings: The Classic Guide to Strategy	61:Miyamoto Musashi	62:1988	64:Gramercy	68:read	69:2017-09-16	63:9780517415283	67:3/5	70:An interesting book, though more like a collection of thoughts squished together than an outright book. Some of the parts are very basic and I found myself almost skimming ahead. Other parts are wonderfully philosophical. I think it'll make a nice reference book.\n\nSecond reading: I moved this down to three stars. It relies heavily on the contradictory patterns in Buddhist philosophy at the expense of much content. There are just a few parts with direct information of value to strategy and mindset.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/867247
