5:000887877	6:gr-887877	3:Red Seas Under Red Skies (Gentleman Bastard, #2)	4:book review	60:Red Seas Under Red Skies (Gentleman Bastard, #2)	61:Scott Lynch	62:2007	64:Bantam Spectra	68:read	69:2014-03-21	63:9780553804683	67:2/5	70:This book almost lost me halfway through when the plot took a sudden turn and headed to sea. Unlike the first book I had a much harder time getting into the story and really investing myself this time around. It took such a significant amount of time that when the book suddenly turned and changed I was really angry and frustrated. I actually put the book down for a few weeks before I worked up the energy to continue.\n\nI'm glad I did, though, as the story at sea was much stronger and more engaging than the beginning. \n\nOverall, this book was worth about half as much as book 1, but it was nice to spend time with the characters again. Moving on to book 3 now. I really hope it's better than #2.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/887877
