5:009647532	6:gr-9647532	3:Fuzzy Nation (Fuzzy Sapiens, #7)	4:book review	60:Fuzzy Nation (Fuzzy Sapiens, #7)	61:John Scalzi	62:2011	64:Tor Books	68:read	69:2020-09-04	63:9780765328540	67:5/5	70:Wow! This was a really great story all around. I'm especially happy that it was a re-telling of a book that otherwise would have been stained by the time it was authored. How many books and films will go that way, I wonder? How wonderful it will be to have this as an example of how a great story can be reframed for a new audience.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/9647532
