5:009895316	6:gr-9895316	3:たけくらべ [Takekurabe]	4:book review	60:たけくらべ [Takekurabe]	61:Ichiyō Higuchi	62:2010	64:Hakkōjo Hōmusha :Hatsubaimoto Shūeisha	68:read	69:2022-01-18	63:9784834263398	67:5/5	70:Wow! This was wonderful. The characters are so sharp and real in such a short work, and their character feels as modern as any today. I'm utterly fascinated by the setting and the childish gangs. That alone would be enough but then we have Midori and a powerful glimpse into that tragic step beyond childhood which we all must suffer. This work is truly a timeless gem.	71:https://www.goodreads.com/book/show/9895316
